snippet.title: Ratten Reich - Exclusive Gameplay Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2022
snippet.description:
This exclusive gameplay trailer for Ratten Reich shows off its real-time strategy game mechanics where you must command your army of rat troops to survive the ongoing war. Take a look at the rts mechanics in Ratten Reich set in the World War II setting.
